주요 관계
Project      -[:CONTAINS]->       Module
Module       -[:CONTAINS]->       Package
Package      -[:CONTAINS]->       SourceFile
SourceFile   -[:DECLARES]->       JavaType
JavaType     -[:HAS_METHOD]->     Method
JavaType     -[:INJECTS]->        JavaType
JavaType     -[:IMPLEMENTS]->     JavaType
Method       -[:CALLS]->          Method
ApiEndpoint  -[:HANDLED_BY]->     Method
Method       -[:READS_FROM]->     DatabaseTable
Method       -[:WRITES_TO]->      DatabaseTable
Mapper       -[:MAPS_TO]->        DatabaseTable
JavaType     -[:USES_DTO]->       DTO
JavaType     -[:CONFORMS_TO]->    StandardRule
JavaType     -[:VIOLATES]->       StandardRule
Chunk        -[:DESCRIBES]->      JavaType
Chunk        -[:EVIDENCE_FOR]->   관계 또는 분석 결과
Generation   -[:BASED_ON]->       StandardRule
각 노드와 관계에는 다음 정보가 필요합니다.
